data.title: Lilli Palmer Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Lilli Palmer on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Lilli Palmer including The Boys from Brazil, De Sade, and more.
data.text: Poised, sophisticated leading lady who arrived in Paris from her native Germany in 1932 and eventually landed in England, where she made her screen debut in 1935. Palmer touched down in Hollywood in 1945 with her first husband, actor Rex Harrison, and returned to Europe nine years later, where she continued to appear in a number of international features.
